{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.011.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h2 class=\"ms1\">LES ROIS DE JUDA ET LES ROIS D\u2019ISRA\u00cbL,<\/h2>\n<h3 class=\"ms2\">DEPUIS LA DIVISION DU ROYAUME JUSQU\u2019\u00c0 JOSAPHAT, ROI DE JUDA, ET ACHAB, ROI D\u2019ISRA\u00cbL<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"mr\">Ch. 12 \u00e0 22. (2 Ch 10 \u00e0 20.) (Os 4:15-17; 6:10, 11.)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">Division du royaume: Roboam roi de Juda, J\u00e9roboam roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-24: cf. 2 Ch 10; 11:1-12. Pr 3:7. Os 13:11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Roboam se rendit \u00e0 Sichem, car tout Isra\u00ebl \u00e9tait venu \u00e0 Sichem pour le faire roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2","name":"1 Rois 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.11.43","name":"1 Rois 11:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.11.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Lorsque J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, eut des nouvelles, il \u00e9tait encore en \u00c9gypte, o\u00f9 il s\u2019\u00e9tait enfui loin du roi Salomon, et c\u2019\u00e9tait en \u00c9gypte qu\u2019il demeurait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3","name":"1 Rois 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.1","name":"1 Rois 12:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>On l\u2019envoya appeler. Alors J\u00e9roboam et toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl vinrent \u00e0 Roboam et lui parl\u00e8rent ainsi:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4","name":"1 Rois 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2","name":"1 Rois 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ton p\u00e8re a rendu notre joug dur; toi maintenant, all\u00e8ge cette rude servitude et le joug pesant que nous a impos\u00e9 ton p\u00e8re. Et nous te servirons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5","name":"1 Rois 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3","name":"1 Rois 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il leur dit: Allez, et revenez vers moi dans trois jours. Et le peuple s\u2019en alla.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6","name":"1 Rois 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4","name":"1 Rois 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le roi Roboam consulta les vieillards qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 aupr\u00e8s de Salomon, son p\u00e8re, pendant sa vie, et il dit: Que conseillez-vous de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 ce peuple?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7","name":"1 Rois 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5","name":"1 Rois 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et voici ce qu\u2019ils lui dirent: Si aujourd\u2019hui tu rends service \u00e0 ce peuple, si tu leur c\u00e8des, et si tu leur r\u00e9ponds par des paroles bienveillantes, ils seront pour toujours tes serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8","name":"1 Rois 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6","name":"1 Rois 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mais Roboam laissa le conseil que lui donnaient les vieillards, et il consulta les jeunes gens qui avaient grandi avec lui et qui l\u2019entouraient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9","name":"1 Rois 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7","name":"1 Rois 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il leur dit: Que conseillez-vous de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 ce peuple qui me tient ce langage: All\u00e8ge le joug que nous a impos\u00e9 ton p\u00e8re?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10","name":"1 Rois 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8","name":"1 Rois 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Et voici ce que lui dirent les jeunes gens qui avaient grandi avec lui: Tu parleras ainsi \u00e0 ce peuple qui t\u2019a tenu ce langage: Ton p\u00e8re a rendu notre joug pesant, et toi, all\u00e8ge-le-nous! Tu leur parleras ainsi: Mon petit doigt est plus gros que les reins de mon p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11","name":"1 Rois 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9","name":"1 Rois 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Maintenant, mon p\u00e8re vous a charg\u00e9s d\u2019un joug pesant, et moi je vous le rendrai plus pesant; mon p\u00e8re vous a ch\u00e2ti\u00e9s avec des fouets, et moi je vous ch\u00e2tierai avec des scorpions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12","name":"1 Rois 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10","name":"1 Rois 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam et tout le peuple vinrent \u00e0 Roboam le troisi\u00e8me jour, suivant ce qu\u2019avait dit le roi: Revenez vers moi dans trois jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13","name":"1 Rois 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11","name":"1 Rois 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le roi r\u00e9pondit durement au peuple. Il laissa le conseil que lui avaient donn\u00e9 les vieillards,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14","name":"1 Rois 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12","name":"1 Rois 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>et il leur parla ainsi d\u2019apr\u00e8s le conseil des jeunes gens: Mon p\u00e8re a rendu votre joug pesant, et moi je vous le rendrai plus pesant; mon p\u00e8re vous a ch\u00e2ti\u00e9s avec des fouets, et moi je vous ch\u00e2tierai avec des scorpions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15","name":"1 Rois 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13","name":"1 Rois 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ainsi le roi n\u2019\u00e9couta point le peuple; car cela fut dirig\u00e9 par l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en vue de l\u2019accomplissement de la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite par Achija de Silo \u00e0 J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16","name":"1 Rois 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14","name":"1 Rois 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Lorsque tout Isra\u00ebl vit que le roi ne l\u2019\u00e9coutait pas, le peuple r\u00e9pondit au roi: Quelle part avons-nous avec David? Nous n\u2019avons point d\u2019h\u00e9ritage avec le fils d\u2019Isa\u00ef! A tes tentes, Isra\u00ebl! Maintenant, pourvois \u00e0 ta maison, David! Et Isra\u00ebl s\u2019en alla dans ses tentes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17","name":"1 Rois 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15","name":"1 Rois 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui habitaient les villes de Juda furent les seuls sur qui r\u00e9gna Roboam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18","name":"1 Rois 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16","name":"1 Rois 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Alors le roi Roboam envoya Adoram, qui \u00e9tait pr\u00e9pos\u00e9 aux imp\u00f4ts. Mais Adoram fut lapid\u00e9 par tout Isra\u00ebl, et il mourut. Et le roi Roboam se h\u00e2ta de monter sur un char, pour s\u2019enfuir \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19","name":"1 Rois 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17","name":"1 Rois 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019est d\u00e9tach\u00e9 de la maison de David jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20","name":"1 Rois 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18","name":"1 Rois 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Tout Isra\u00ebl ayant appris que J\u00e9roboam \u00e9tait de retour, ils l\u2019envoy\u00e8rent appeler dans l\u2019assembl\u00e9e, et ils le firent roi sur tout Isra\u00ebl. La tribu de Juda fut la seule qui suivit la maison de David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21","name":"1 Rois 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19","name":"1 Rois 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Roboam, arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, rassembla toute la maison de Juda et la tribu de Benjamin, cent quatre-vingt mille hommes d\u2019\u00e9lite propres \u00e0 la guerre, pour qu\u2019ils combattissent contre la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl afin de la ramener sous la domination de Roboam, fils de Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22","name":"1 Rois 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20","name":"1 Rois 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais la parole de Dieu fut ainsi adress\u00e9e \u00e0 Schemaeja, homme de Dieu:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23","name":"1 Rois 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21","name":"1 Rois 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Parle \u00e0 Roboam, fils de Salomon, roi de Juda, et \u00e0 toute la maison de Juda et de Benjamin, et au reste du peuple. Et dis-leur:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24","name":"1 Rois 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22","name":"1 Rois 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Ne montez point, et ne faites pas la guerre \u00e0 vos fr\u00e8res, les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! Que chacun de vous retourne dans sa maison, car c\u2019est de par moi que cette chose est arriv\u00e9e. Ils ob\u00e9irent \u00e0 la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et ils s\u2019en retourn\u00e8rent, selon la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25","name":"1 Rois 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23","name":"1 Rois 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le royaume d\u2019Isra\u00ebl sous J\u00e9roboam. Culte des veaux d\u2019or<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-33: cf. Ex 32:1-8. (2 R 17:21, 22. 2 Ch 11:13-17.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam b\u00e2tit Sichem sur la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, et il y demeura; puis il en sortit, et b\u00e2tit Penuel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26","name":"1 Rois 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24","name":"1 Rois 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam dit en son c\u0153ur: Le royaume pourrait bien maintenant retourner \u00e0 la maison de David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27","name":"1 Rois 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25","name":"1 Rois 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Si ce peuple monte \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem pour faire des sacrifices dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le c\u0153ur de ce peuple retournera \u00e0 son seigneur, \u00e0 Roboam, roi de Juda, et ils me tueront et retourneront \u00e0 Roboam, roi de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28","name":"1 Rois 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26","name":"1 Rois 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre consult\u00e9, le roi fit deux veaux d\u2019or, et il dit au peuple: Assez longtemps vous \u00eates mont\u00e9s \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem; Isra\u00ebl! voici ton Dieu, qui t\u2019a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29","name":"1 Rois 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27","name":"1 Rois 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Il pla\u00e7a l\u2019un de ces veaux \u00e0 B\u00e9thel, et il mit l\u2019autre \u00e0 Dan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30","name":"1 Rois 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28","name":"1 Rois 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Ce fut l\u00e0 une occasion de p\u00e9ch\u00e9. Le peuple alla devant l\u2019un des veaux jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Dan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31","name":"1 Rois 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29","name":"1 Rois 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam fit une maison de hauts lieux, et il cr\u00e9a des sacrificateurs pris parmi tout le peuple et n\u2019appartenant point aux fils de L\u00e9vi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32","name":"1 Rois 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30","name":"1 Rois 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Il \u00e9tablit une f\u00eate au huiti\u00e8me mois, le quinzi\u00e8me jour du mois, comme la f\u00eate qui se c\u00e9l\u00e9brait en Juda, et il offrit des sacrifices sur l\u2019autel. Voici ce qu\u2019il fit \u00e0 B\u00e9thel afin que l\u2019on sacrifi\u00e2t aux veaux qu\u2019il avait faits. Il pla\u00e7a \u00e0 B\u00e9thel les pr\u00eatres des hauts lieux qu\u2019il avait \u00e9lev\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33","name":"1 Rois 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31","name":"1 Rois 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 12:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.12.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Et il monta sur l\u2019autel qu\u2019il avait fait \u00e0 B\u00e9thel, le quinzi\u00e8me jour du huiti\u00e8me mois, mois qu\u2019il avait choisi de son gr\u00e9. Il fit une f\u00eate pour les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et il monta sur l\u2019autel pour br\u00fbler des parfums.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12","name":"1 Rois 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1","name":"1 Rois 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32","name":"1 Rois 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb3443e17.74748299');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3443e17.74748299\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb3443e17.74748299","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb3443e17.74748299'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3443e17.74748299\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}